            "title": "黑期輕微低水約20點 重磅港股ADR升跌不一",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時16升55點或0.23%，報24265點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報24306點，較香港上日現貨收市高22點或0.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣510.3元，較上日香港收市低2.67元或0.52%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣111.9元，較上日香港收市低0.16元或0.14%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣129.5元，較上日香港收市高0.09元或0.07%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣129.8元，較上日香港收市低0.5元或0.38%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣59.4元，較上日香港收市高0.48元或0.81%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣95.5元，較上日香港收市高0.49元或0.51%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣71.7元，較上日香港收市高0.15元或0.21%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣421.8元，較上日香港收市高0.58元或0.14%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣50.7元，較上日香港收市高0.31元或0.62%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣8元，較上日香港收市低0.02元或0.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市7月份期指收報24182點，跌67點，較上日恒指收市24284點，低水102點。7月份科指期貨夜市收報5325點，較上日科指收市低水16點；7月份國指期貨夜市收報8719點，較上日國指收市低水43點。</p>\n</div>",
